name: Baby's First Christmas Onesie Ornament
description:
This baby's first Christmas ornament will be surely be a keepsake for years to come! It is hand sawed out of 14g metal, and will not break or get ruined like a standard glass ornament, therefore making a sturdy addition to your ornament collection!

~I have hand sawed this onesie out of 14 g aluminum, and it will not tarnish or rust.
~It is hand stamped with the birth details you give me, and your choice of ribbon is attached to the tops of the piece to let it hang nicely from your Christmas tree!
~The ornament has been given a brushed look, and the edges of it have been filed and sanded as to not cut or poke fingers. 
It measures right at 3" (not including the ribbon).

ORDERING:
1) Please choose the ribbon color from the dropdown box 
2) Leave the following birth details in the note to seller box
 - First & middle name *OR* first & last name
 - date of birth
 - birth weight (lbs & oz)
 - height
 - time of birth


These are hand-made to order, please allow up to 3 full weeks for production time.

Metals Used: 
Aluminum 
Stainless Steel

name: Autism/Puzzle Personalized Ornament
description:
I love the Christmas season and decorating our Christmas tree! Growing up my family would do the whole tree-experience. Going and picking out our tree, cutting it down, taking the traditional tree picture, getting cider, and then the entire getting it home and setting it up process. We'd thread popcorn and cranberries and spend hours putting up the ornaments. Good memories. 

I have created this ornament for you to add to your tree! 

The edge puzzle piece has been hand sawed out of aluminum, and stamped with a cute phrase "I've found my missing piece". It also has been personalized with a name and a blue ribbon is used to hang it from the tree.
The ornament has been given a brushed look, and the edges of it have been filed and sanded as to not cut or poke fingers.
It measures about 2 3/4" (not including the ribbon).

When ordering, please leave the NAME you want the ornament personalized with. 

These are hand-made to order, please allow up to 3 full weeks for production time.

Metals Used:
Aluminum
Stainless Steel
